<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
    <head>
        <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
        <title>Reset your password</title>
        <style type="text/css">
        body {margin: 0; padding: 0; min-width: 100%!important;}
        .content {width: 100%; max-width: 600px;}  
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <p>Hi,</p>
        <p>You recently asked to renew your password. Please click on the following link to enter your new password : </p>
        <p><a href="http://<%= host %>/password_renew?token=<%= updatePasswordToken %>">https://<%= host %>/password_renew?token=<%= updatePasswordToken %></a></p>
        <p>This link will be available during the next 60 minuts.</p>
        <p>If you are not at the origin of this message please ignore it.</p>
        <p>Regards</p>
    </body>
</html>